                    <h2 style="color: #051cb2!important;">Redmil Group<strong>Regd Office</strong></h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Address:</strong>1st floor, STFC Club, 86/245,Eldeco Garden Estate, Raipurwa<br />
                            Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh-208003
                        </li>
                        <li ><strong>Contact No:</strong> (+91) 81-91-92-93-94 (Monday to Saturday, 10:00 AM to 6:30 PM)</li>
                        <li ><strong>Email ID:</strong> info@redmil.in</li>


                    </ul>
                    <hr>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="bg-border">
